{"type": "article", "id": 24736, "title": "圆锥吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121850mhy0oBE5jVATYSzv.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是意大利设计师 Roberto Paoli 为灯具品牌 ModoLuce 设计的吊灯，他使用了非常简洁的圆锥形。三种吊灯的开合角度不一样，拼凑在一起却增加了活泼的气氛。圆锥灯罩的上面横着放一个圆片，从侧面看就像是一条短的直线，隐隐与下面的圆锥构成了一种平衡，突出了吊灯本身的几何感。有 6 种颜色选择，<a href=\"http://www.modoluce.com/#/collezioni/sospensione/201601\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121848usk06qE2eil5oL9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121849KmojPZBWze2NIutQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071218499sOLPoQJNHDyxV32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23919308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}